name: Chewbacca, Protector (V)
Lore: 'Chewie honored his life debt to Han by protecting Leia. Posed as the mercenary Snoova while on Coruscant. Smuggler. Wookiee.',
Text: 'Deploys free to Coruscant and is a spy while there. During your deploy phase, may deploy one Boushh or Vibro-Ax (on Chewie) from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While with Leia, her game text may not be canceled and, once per turn, may take the bottom card of Force Pile into hand.',
